<div class="image"><img src="images/health.jpg" height=150px /></div>
<p class="txt" align="right"><b>What is Health Insurance?</b></p>
<p style="font-size:20px"><strong>Health Insurance</strong> is an insurance policy that ensures that you get cashless treatment or expense reimbursement, in case you fall ill. It is a contract between a general insurance company and an individual, which provides coverage for the expenses incurred when availing healthcare or medical treatment at the hospital. However, the insurance company would pay for your treatment if the medical condition/emergency is covered by your policy..</p>

