<h1 style="font-size:36px" align="right">Home Insurance</h1>



<img src="images/home.jpg" align="right">
<b><p class="txt1" align="left">What is Home Insurance?</p></b>
<p style="font-size:20px"><b>Home insurance</b>, also commonly called hazard insurance or homeowner's insurance , is a type of property insurance that covers a private residence.It is an insurance policy that combines various personal insurance protections, which can include losses occurring to one's home, its contents, loss of use,or loss of other personal possessions of the homeowner.as well as liability insurance for accidents that may happen at the home or at the hands of the homeowner within the policy territory.
</p>
</div>
