<div class="body-container">

<div class="welcome">
<h1 style="font-size:36px" align="left">Vehicle Insurance</h1>

<div class="image"><img src="images/vehicle.jpg" /></div>
<b><p class="txt" align="left"> What is Vehicle Insurance?</p></b>
<p style="font-size:20px"><b>Vehicle insurance</b> (also known as car insurance, motor insurance or auto insurance) is insurance purchased for cars, trucks, motorcycles, and other road vehicles. Its primary use is to provide financial protection against physical damage and/or bodily injury resulting from traffic collisions. To a lesser degree vehicle insurance may additionally offer financial protection against theft of the vehicle and possibly damage to the vehicle, sustained from things other than traffic collisions.

</p>
</div>
</div>
